<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>YRAN Community</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    header {
      background: #2c7a7b;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav {
      background: #205e5f;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: block;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      background: #184a4b;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: #e6fffa;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .section {
      margin-top: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    footer {
      background: #2c7a7b;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Young Resilient Advocacy Network (YRAN)</h1>
  <p>Empowering Youth. Driving Change.</p>
</header>

<nav>
  <a href="#">Home</a>
  <a href="#about">About</a>
  <a href="#programs">Programs</a>
  <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

  <div class="hero">
    <h2>Welcome to YRAN</h2>
    <p>We empower young people through advocacy, climate action, and economic opportunities.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="about" class="section">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>YRAN is a youth-led organization based in Mathare focused on empowering adolescent girls and young women through SRHR, climate change awareness, and economic empowerment.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="programs" class="section">
    <h2>Our Programs</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Climate Change Awareness</li>
      <li>Sexual and Reproductive Health Rights (SRHR)</li>
      <li>Economic Empowerment Projects</li>
      <li>Recycling and Plastic Art Hub</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div id="contact" class="section">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: info@yran.org</p>
    <p>Phone: +254 700 000000</p>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2026 YRAN. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
